# Blog platform

inspiration: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lh7EBoiRRfQ

## Requirements
- XAMPP server

## Quick start (Part 1)
clone the repository into the xampp server htdocs folder.

### If using MYSQL as database
from sql folder take stoa.sql and import it into phpmyadmin

### ELSE IF using Wordpress api
showing usage of wordpress api in api_test.php

## Quick Start (Part 2)

goto: http://localhost/stoa

Don't worry about passwords. Not verifying those ;)

enjoy!